CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 10, 1966, pg. 1B reads: "The Honda Kid - Adorable Cheryle Beaman was not afraid to tackle this miniature Honda. In fact she was quite the "Honda Kid" on the toy motor bike."
TitMainTitle: Cheryle Beaman mounting Honda 50 pedal scooter in front of display of pedal cars and wagons with Christmas decorations in Toyland on ninth floor of Kaufmann's Department Store
